Additional details

The Cisco Business CBS220-24T-4G switch is simple and affordable smart switch for business-class network. CBS220 series bridge the gap between the affordability of an unmanaged device and the ease-of-use of smart switches. With their intuitive dashboard, mobile app support, and multiple Power over Ethernet (PoE) options, these switches deliver a solid business network.

      Great hardware. Working great. A little complicated to configure, but manageable.
      Reviewed in the United States on March 28, 2022

      Bought this for a new site, needed one that can do gigabit and POE. This one does both for ALL ports. It also has 4 1GB SFP connections, so I can always connect out to others via fiber if needed. However, the configuration can be a little convoluted, even thought it does... See more
      Bought this for a new site, needed one that can do gigabit and POE. This one does both for ALL ports. It also has 4 1GB SFP connections, so I can always connect out to others via fiber if needed. However, the configuration can be a little convoluted, even thought it does have a GUI. Just go nice and slow and look things up to make sure you do it right. You mess up your VLANs and you could lock yourself out.

      ONE BIG NOTE: MAKE SURE YOU CHANGE BOTH THE USERNAME AND THE PASSWORD. Leaving either one of them "cisco" and it will not work properly and you will need to reset the switch to factory defaults and start over.

      Ours is currently running two basic VLANs and about 18 devices, 10 of which are POE. It's working great and having no issues.

      For the price, these are great and whats even better: NO LICENSING FEES!!!
